name: Benches knows everything…
description: The benches are the beginning of the conversation. From the moment they are made, they seem to have thought of romances, indifferences, sittings, solving tables,chess elephants and horses, and even homeless people who rest on them. The conversation between cold bodies and metal! The conversation of smoky cigarettes, the conversation of the smell of freshly mown grass with the smell of wet paint, the conversation of wet from rain and heat from the sun, and the conversation of shadows and coolness… Benches are created for conversation, whether they are filled or empty; They speak the language of the resting. Whether they are black and white, or colorful...
